{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[F#]Now
The [D]mist across the win[E]dow hides the lines[F#]
But [D]nothing hides the co[E]lor of the lights[C#m]   that [D]shine
[E] Electrici[C#m]ty so [D]fine
Look and dry[E] your eyes
{end_of_verse}


