{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[F#]We
So [D]tired of all the dark[E]ness in our lives[F#]
With [D]no more angry words[E] to say can come[C#m]   alive[D]
[E] Get into a [C#m]car and [D]drive
To the o[E]ther side
{end_of_verse}


